Common.Strapline.Common.Text: FUNCTIONAL SHOWROOM & WAREHOUSE – SUB LEASE OR NEW DIRECT LEASE

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
411sqm Office & showroom area
1,328sqm Workshop & warehouse facility 
Over 4,000sqm of designated hardstand 
Multiple roller doors
Good access and truck turning 
Three phase power supply
Available Now
 
Archerfield is located in the heart of Brisbane’s southern industrial corridor, approximately 10 kilometres south of the Brisbane CBD. Archerfield is an established industrial precinct well serviced by the Ipswich Motorway and Beaudesert Road.

For further information or to arrange an inspection please contact CBRE the Exclusive Agents.

999 Beaudesert Road, Archerfield boasts a large prominent corner site with full exposure and ease of access via both Beaudesert and Boundary Roads.

The site is improved by a functional warehouse/workshop facility fitted with a near new modern air conditioned office and sales accommodation. The site’s biggest statement includes a large fully secured concreted hardstand/ sales yard area that wraps the entire corner of Beaudesert and Boundary Roads. 

Features of Tenancy 2 include:

+ 720sqm* Service Pit
+ 41sqm* Storage Mezzanine 
+ 100sqm* Office & Spare Parts  
+ 1,300sqm* Hardstand / sales yard
+ 2,161sqm* Total Area 
+ Large three phase power

Situated approximately 13 radial km south of the CBD with direct access to Pacific Motorway & Ipswich Motorway. 

Adjoining S-E Queensland Motorway’s Include:
+ Centenary Highway
+ Gateway Motorway
+ Logan Motorway
+ Mt Lindesay Highway
+ Cunningham Highway

Known as one of Brisbane busiest roads, the area has a constant demand to high profile occupiers and as a result holds host to some of Australia’s most recognised companies.

For more information or to book an inspection, please contact Marketing Agents
